settings.content:
Award-winning design that combines style, tech, and travel efficiency more than just a rolling box for your things.

Key Features:

  • Zipperless TSA Lock System
  • Front Laptop Pocket
  • Built-In Cup + Phone Holder
  • USB + USB-C Charging Port
  • Unbreakable Polycarbonate Shell
  • 360° Smooth Spinner Wheels
  • Interior Compression System
  • Water-resistant Toiletry Pocket + Passport Sleeve
  • Packs for 5–7 Day Trips
  • Airline-Approved Carry-On Size
